目標<br />\n做咩忽然個個中左幻術咁睇唔開<br />\n當係為左救未來既千千萬萬個手足<br />\n停止歪風由你做起<br />\n我地一齊走落去<br />\n贏就一齊贏<br />\n就算最後真係輸<br />\n咪一齊坐監囉<br />\n一齊係入面唱歌囉<br />\n做咩要拋棄手足？"},{"pid":"91ff12d824432e8e15dc233b3b10b256b10c3849","tid":1550944,"uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T21:03:06.000Z","msg":"喂 我地約左聽日中環見架"},{"pid":"d8e7239e775d6c1be528e6c6c69b1679eb30bff5","tid":1550944,"uid":308262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:56:14.000Z","msg":"我哋需要你呀！講好咗一齊食晒4餸1湯，依家得個湯到咗，梗係食埋落去啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有呀，我哋相約咗有一日喺煲底除口罩相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 你肚餓未呀？不如一齊食早餐先<br />\n利申：南區巴"},{"pid":"9009a69d2802e3cd7f650f308fa235d69d3f2a40","tid":1550944,"uid":267295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:38:29.000Z","msg":"喂，其實我都係喎，因為安慰人去堅強，要開心，係一啲大道理黎，唔會有錯，但知易行難，正如你肚餓，我會去叫你食飯，但係點樣去令你食得開心係另一個難題黎<br />\n<br />\n教人去堅強去開心係一個大方向，點樣去令到人地同自己開心係一啲細節，會有好多唔同既野去影響左件事既效果，更何況當局者迷，未必可以好理性抽身去處理到自己既問題"},{"pid":"354427b505448d6ceb43c75ef616932aebb78041","tid":1550944,"uid":175799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66beb8e8a1b50d8604704e2711a20f65e141ca3","tid":1550944,"uid":164523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a87be695baecb24c21946c3c78fd2e97f2fe9dfe","tid":1550944,"uid":318525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faa0cbdd53c4e596c2ec8ccd09b8e14740d430bc","tid":1550944,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:31:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/WearehereHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWearehereHK&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=f9ea099e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WearehereHK</a><br />\n如果你係南區人我唔介意而家出嚟陪你"},"citedBy":2,"reply